   :kind :storage-contract
   :based-on ["doc/project/40-proposals/065-local-relationship-layer.md"
              "doc/project/60-solutions/028-temporal-storage-convention/028-temporal-storage-convention.md"]
   :schemas []
   :responsibilities
   ["Maintain rebuildable SQLite projection per Solution 028 three-table shape"
    "Hold no plaintext relationship state on disk in target state"
    "Use encrypted-at-rest cell-level AEAD with per-store key derived from vault as first-iteration target"
    "Permit opaque references with tx/id offsets as acceptable interim shape"
    "Treat existing `local-contacts.sqlite` plaintext store as labelled transitional only"
    "Apply performance-profile cadence for snapshot recheckpoint (minimal: 50/30s, balanced: 100/60s, full-audit: 25/15s)"]
   :status :partial
   :notes "Daemon projection exists with transactions, events, current_classes, current_memberships, current_nym_bindings, predicates, and decisions. Projection cells are not yet encrypted-at-rest, so this remains partial."}

