  {:cap/id :load-bearing-invariants
   :title "Load-Bearing Invariants"
   :kind :architecture-contract
   :based-on ["doc/project/40-proposals/065-local-relationship-layer.md"]
   :schemas []
   :responsibilities
   ["Enforce label != authority: class membership never grants capability by itself"
    "Keep classes and memberships separate entities; never conflate"
    "Enforce strictly local-emitted membership facts; no wire-shape inbound"
    "Reserve class IDs `contacts` and `friends`; require namespace for others"
    "Treat `blocked` as status, never as class"
    "Archive classes never delete; facts remain in event log"
    "Make class definitions mutable projection with every change emitting an append-only fact"
    "Enforce relationship-derived node trust requires membership + binding + policy + caps + bounded effects"
